  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/09/snapchat-responds-to-privacy-scares/\"><img alt=\"Snapchat 5 for iOS\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/www.engadget.com/media/2013/06/snapchat-5-ios.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在 460 万用户信息<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/01/snapchat-user-info-leak/\">泄漏</a>后，Snapchat 终于在今天迈出了填补漏洞的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/03/snapchat-hack-response/\">第一步</a>。在其新版的 Android、iOS 应用中，用户可以解除账户与手机号码间的关联，防止隐私进一步外泄。除此之外，为了避免信息被滥用，用户在使用寻找好友功能时将必须要核实手机号码。当然，这样的解决方案并不完美，只能期望 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/snapchat\">Snapchat</a> 接下来能想出更好的办法吧。亡羊补牢这种事... 哎...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/09/snapchat-responds-to-privacy-scares/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blog.snapchat.com/post/72768002320/find-friends-improvements\" target=\"_blank\">Snapchat Blog</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/snapchat/id447188370?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.snapchat.android\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/09/snapchat-responds-to-privacy-scares/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20804515/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/09/snapchat-responds-to-privacy-scares/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
